 \theta = \frac{2 \pi}{n}. 
 AB \sin \left(\angle BAC\right) = BC \Rightarrow \frac{d}{2} \sin\left(\frac{\pi}{n}\right) = \frac{m}{2} \Rightarrow d = \frac{m}{\sin \left(\pi / n\right)}. 
